<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <!--title>Control Panel - Room <%= roomId %></title-->
    <title>Between What's SEEN & UNSEEN</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300..700;1,300..700&family=Nunito+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..12,200..1000;1,6..12,200..1000&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
</head>
<body>
    <section>
        <header>
            <img src="images/General Icons.svg" alt="">
            <img src="images/Logomark.svg" alt="">
            <div style="width: 28px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
        </header>
        <!--h1>Control Panel - Room <%= roomId %></h1-->
        
        <div class="body">
            <div class="body__1" style="_display: none;">
                <div class="body__1__1"><img src="images/Logo.svg" alt=""></div>
                <div class="body__1__2">Beauty is not just seen.
                    <br>It's also unseen.</div>
                <div>
                    <button id="btnStart">GET STARTED</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="visibility: hidden;_display: none;" class="body__2">
                <form id="textObjectForm">
                    <div>
                        <h2>What’s a sense of 
                            <br>beauty you’ve noticed 
                            <br>recently?</h2>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <!--label for="title">Title:</label-->
                            <input type="text" id="title" name="title" placeholder="Your name" maxlength="20" required>
                            <span class="char-counter"><span id="title-count">0</span>/20</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <!--label for="content">Content:</label-->
                            <textarea id="content" name="content" rows="7" placeholder="Write your beauty quote..." maxlength="100" required></textarea>
                            <span class="char-counter"><span id="content-count">0</span>/100</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Your words will become part of a live archive. 
                            <br>You’ll also receive your own beauty quote wallpaper.</p>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" id="submit-btn" disabled>SUBMIT</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div style="visibility: hidden;_display: none;" class="body__3">
                <div class="body__3__1">
                    <canvas id="thankYouCanvas" width="82" width="178"></canvas>
                </div>
                <div class="body__3__2">
                    <h2>Thank you for sharing.</h2>
                    <p>Your words are now part of the live archive.
                        <br>Carry your beauty with you — 
                        <br>download as a wallpaper.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="body__3__3">
                    <button id="randomButton" class="img-btn"><img src="images/Button.svg" alt=""></button>
                    <button id="refreshButton" class="img-btn"><img src="images/Button refresh.svg" alt=""></button>
                    <button id="saveButton">SAVE</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="visibility: hidden;_display: none;" class="body__4">
                <h2>About This Site</h2>
                <p>Welcome to the Seen & Unseen mobile experience — a part of an experimental design project exploring personal perception, emotion, and the aesthetics of self-expression. This platform invites you to share your own quote or reflection, which will be projected in real-time on our desktop exhibition site.</p>
                <p>Please note: this is a non-commercial, academic project developed solely for study purposes. All content shared here is part of a temporary, creative exploration and will not be used for profit, advertising, or data collection. Your contributions remain anonymous and will not be stored after the exhibition period.</p>
                <p>By continuing, you agree to participate in this artistic research experiment. Thank you for being part of this moment of shared beauty — where your words become part of a collective reflection.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="controls">
            <button id="addBox">Add Box</button>
            <button id="addCircle">Add Circle</button>
            <button id="addDonut">Add Quarter Donut</button>
            <button id="toggleAutoExpand">Auto-Expand: ON</button>
        </div>

        <footer>
            &copy;2025 SENSO LAB Ltd.
        </footer>
    </section>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/socket.io/4.0.1/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.13.0/dist/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/index.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/index-page.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/index-thankyou.js"></script>
</body>
</html>